jobs.Description:
Hot water pressure is too low in third floor bathroom.
 
 
John Doidge (17/09/2025) - Work Note
Test operation of the basin taps and the shower in room 49. The basin taps appear to have the same flow and pressure. The shower, when turned to a hotter temperature isn’t as powerful as it should be. This shower is fed from a shower pump at the far end of the third floor corridor. This shower pump also feeds 4 other showers. With the shower in room 49 running, the shower pump does not come on. Test the other showers to find that the pump only operates when the closest 2 showers are used. This is probably due to the distance from the pump to the furtherest outlet and the restricted flow through the 15mm hoses to the pump.
An alternative pump has been identified and will be ordered.
jobs.descriptionText: Hot water pressure is too low in third floor bathroom.  John Doidge (17/09/2025) - Work NoteTest operation of the basin taps and the shower in room 49. This shower is fed from a shower pump at the far end of the third floor corridor. This shower pump also feeds 4 other showers. With the shower in room 49 running, the shower pump does not come on. Test the other showers to find that the pump only operates when the closest 2 showers are used. This is probably due to the distance from the pump to the furtherest outlet and the restricted flow through the 15mm hoses to the pump.An alternative pump has been identified and will be ordered.

jobs.Description:
East corridor cleaners cupboard cold tap is not working.
 
 
John Doidge (17/09/2025) - Work Note
1/4 turn bib tap found isolated. Re-instate the supply and test operation of the tap. With the water supply on, the tap runs even when closed and is noisy. Remove the tap insert to service it. The tap is no longer noisy but but still drip, as does the hot tap.
Replacement taps have been ordered.
